const product = $json;

return {
  productId: product.id,
  productName: product.name || '',
  productDescription: (product.description || '').replace(/<[^>]*>/g, '').substring(0, 1500),
  productShortDescription: (product.short_description || '').replace(/<[^>]*>/g, ''),
  productPrice: product.price || '0',
  productRegularPrice: product.regular_price || '0',
  productSalePrice: product.sale_price || '',
  productCategories: (product.categories || []).map(c => c.name).join(', '),
  productTags: (product.tags || []).map(t => t.name).join(', '),
  productImage: product.images?.[0]?.src || '',
  productUrl: product.permalink || '',
  productStatus: product.status || '',
  productStock: product.stock_status || '',
  totalSales: product.total_sales || 0,
  averageRating: product.average_rating || '0',
  ratingCount: product.rating_count || 0
};

- Scores (Overall, Marketability, Name, Description, Pricing, SEO)

- Target audience & marketing angles
